<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: {PAWN_nameDef} spent {PAWN_possessive} entire childhood learning from a master craftsman. {PAWN_pronoun} accumulated valuable experience even though children in the workshop were only permitted to do some basic work. -->
  <Heyra_Story_Apprentice.baseDesc>{PAWN_nameDef}在一位大师工匠门下度过了整个童年。即使工坊里的孩童只被允许做一些杂工，{PAWN_pronoun}仍然积累了宝贵的经验。</Heyra_Story_Apprentice.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: apprentice of a master -->
  <Heyra_Story_Apprentice.title>名师门徒</Heyra_Story_Apprentice.title>
  <!-- EN: apprentice -->
  <Heyra_Story_Apprentice.titleShort>名师门徒</Heyra_Story_Apprentice.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: {PAWN_nameDef} spent {PAWN_possessive} entire childhood learning from a master craftsman. {PAWN_pronoun} accumulated valuable experience even though children in the workshop were only permitted to do some basic work. -->
  <Heyra_Story_ApprenticeD.baseDesc>{PAWN_nameDef}在一位大师工匠门下度过了整个童年。即使工坊里的孩童只被允许做一些杂工，{PAWN_pronoun}仍然积累了宝贵的经验。</Heyra_Story_ApprenticeD.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: apprentice of a master -->
  <Heyra_Story_ApprenticeD.title>名师门徒</Heyra_Story_ApprenticeD.title>
  <!-- EN: apprentice -->
  <Heyra_Story_ApprenticeD.titleShort>名师门徒</Heyra_Story_ApprenticeD.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: {PAWN_nameDef} made armor for Heyran army and the individuals that needed protection. {PAWN_possessive} workshop was small in scale and the equipments were old, but {PAWN_pronoun} worked hard with {PAWN_possessive} assistant to ensure the productivity and quality. -->
  <Heyra_Story_Armorer.baseDesc>{PAWN_nameDef}为寻求装备的人们打造护甲。{PAWN_possessive}的工坊又小又旧，但是{PAWN_pronoun}和助手一起努力保证了产量和质量。</Heyra_Story_Armorer.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: armorer -->
  <Heyra_Story_Armorer.title>铸甲匠</Heyra_Story_Armorer.title>
  <!-- EN: armorer -->
  <Heyra_Story_Armorer.titleShort>铸甲匠</Heyra_Story_Armorer.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: {PAWN_nameDef} showed extraordinary artistic talent at a young age. {PAWN_pronoun} has filled many sketchbooks with {PAWN_possessive} creative drawings. -->
  <Heyra_Story_Artprodigy.baseDesc>{PAWN_nameDef}幼时就展现出惊人的艺术天赋。{PAWN_pronoun}用富有创造力的绘画填满了许多个速写本。</Heyra_Story_Artprodigy.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: art prodigy -->
  <Heyra_Story_Artprodigy.title>绘画逸才</Heyra_Story_Artprodigy.title>
  <!-- EN: art prodigy -->
  <Heyra_Story_Artprodigy.titleShort>绘画逸才</Heyra_Story_Artprodigy.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: {PAWN_nameDef} showed extraordinary artistic talent at a young age. {PAWN_pronoun} has filled many sketchbooks with {PAWN_possessive} creative drawings. -->
  <Heyra_Story_ArtprodigyD.baseDesc>{PAWN_nameDef}幼时就展现出惊人的艺术天赋。{PAWN_pronoun}用富有创造力的绘画填满了许多个速写本。</Heyra_Story_ArtprodigyD.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: art prodigy -->
  <Heyra_Story_ArtprodigyD.title>绘画逸才</Heyra_Story_ArtprodigyD.title>
  <!-- EN: art prodigy -->
  <Heyra_Story_ArtprodigyD.titleShort>绘画逸才</Heyra_Story_ArtprodigyD.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: Born with a beautiful look, {PAWN_nameDef} received countless praises for her cuteness since young. -->
  <Heyra_Story_Attractivechild.baseDesc>{PAWN_nameDef}生得十分美丽，从小就因为可爱的外表受到人们的称赞。</Heyra_Story_Attractivechild.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: attractive child -->
  <Heyra_Story_Attractivechild.title>天生丽质</Heyra_Story_Attractivechild.title>
  <!-- EN: attractive child -->
  <Heyra_Story_Attractivechild.titleShort>天生丽质</Heyra_Story_Attractivechild.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: Born with a beautiful look, {PAWN_nameDef} received countless praises for her cuteness since young. -->
  <Heyra_Story_AttractivechildD.baseDesc>{PAWN_nameDef}生得十分美丽，从小就因为可爱的外表受到人们的称赞。</Heyra_Story_AttractivechildD.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: attractive child -->
  <Heyra_Story_AttractivechildD.title>天生丽质</Heyra_Story_AttractivechildD.title>
  <!-- EN: attractive child -->
  <Heyra_Story_AttractivechildD.titleShort>天生丽质</Heyra_Story_AttractivechildD.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: For various reasons, {PAWN_nameDef} got more love than her sisters combined. However, this also means that {PAWN_pronoun} received more expectations making {PAWN_objective} under pressure far beyond {PAWN_possessive} peers. -->
  <Heyra_Story_Belovedchild.baseDesc>因为种种原因，{PAWN_nameDef}比姐妹们博得了更多的父母的爱。然而这也意味着{PAWN_pronoun}身上寄托了更多的期待，让{PAWN_pronoun}倍感压力。</Heyra_Story_Belovedchild.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: beloved child -->
  <Heyra_Story_Belovedchild.title>掌上明珠</Heyra_Story_Belovedchild.title>
  <!-- EN: beloved child -->
  <Heyra_Story_Belovedchild.titleShort>掌上明珠</Heyra_Story_Belovedchild.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: For various reasons, {PAWN_nameDef} got more love than her sisters combined. However, this also means that {PAWN_pronoun} received more expectations making {PAWN_objective} under pressure far beyond {PAWN_possessive} peers. -->
  <Heyra_Story_BelovedchildD.baseDesc>因为种种原因，{PAWN_nameDef}比姐妹们博得了更多的父母的爱。然而这也意味着{PAWN_pronoun}身上寄托了更多的期待，让{PAWN_pronoun}倍感压力。</Heyra_Story_BelovedchildD.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: beloved child -->
  <Heyra_Story_BelovedchildD.title>掌上明珠</Heyra_Story_BelovedchildD.title>
  <!-- EN: beloved child -->
  <Heyra_Story_BelovedchildD.titleShort>掌上明珠</Heyra_Story_BelovedchildD.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: {PAWN_nameDef} constructed houses for living. {PAWN_pronoun} was stronger than many other workers and could carry parts that will normally require a wheelbarrow to trasport. -->
  <Heyra_Story_Builder.baseDesc>{PAWN_nameDef}的工作就是替人出力盖房。{PAWN_pronoun}比他人更强壮，甚至能扛起一般需要独轮车运输的重物。</Heyra_Story_Builder.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: builder -->
  <Heyra_Story_Builder.title>建筑工</Heyra_Story_Builder.title>
  <!-- EN: builder -->
  <Heyra_Story_Builder.titleShort>建筑工</Heyra_Story_Builder.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: {PAWN_nameDef} was always exhausted by all the works assigned to {PAWN_objective}. She had to hire several servants to take care of the housework. -->
  <Heyra_Story_Busyofficial.baseDesc>{PAWN_nameDef}被工作耗尽了全部精力。{PAWN_pronoun}不得不雇人来替{PAWN_objective}做家务。</Heyra_Story_Busyofficial.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: busy official -->
  <Heyra_Story_Busyofficial.title>繁忙官员</Heyra_Story_Busyofficial.title>
  <!-- EN: official -->
  <Heyra_Story_Busyofficial.titleShort>官员</Heyra_Story_Busyofficial.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: {PAWN_nameDef} owned three cats. {PAWN_pronoun} always made {PAWN_possessive} own homemade cat food with fresh muffalo meat and berries. /n Once a fire took the life of {PAWN_possessive} youngest cat, which traumatized {PAWN_objective} and made {PAWN_objective} pyrophobic ever since. -->
  <Heyra_Story_Catlover.baseDesc>{PAWN_nameDef}有三只猫。{PAWN_pronoun}一直自己制作猫粮，原料一般是新鲜的牛肉和树果。/n以前{PAWN_pronoun}最小的那只猫死在一场火灾中，从那以后{PAWN_pronoun}就对火有阴影。</Heyra_Story_Catlover.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: cat lover -->
  <Heyra_Story_Catlover.title>爱猫人士</Heyra_Story_Catlover.title>
  <!-- EN: cat lover -->
  <Heyra_Story_Catlover.titleShort>爱猫者</Heyra_Story_Catlover.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: {PAWN_nameDef} designed the palaces and gardens for Heyran nobles. {PAWN_pronoun} did not care about the cost and would pursue the pure magnificence with {PAWN_possessive} design.\n		 -->
  <Heyra_Story_Chiefarchitect.baseDesc>{PAWN_nameDef}为皇族设计宫殿和园林。{PAWN_pronoun}的设计不计成本，力求营造极致的壮丽。</Heyra_Story_Chiefarchitect.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: chief architect -->
  <Heyra_Story_Chiefarchitect.title>首席建筑师</Heyra_Story_Chiefarchitect.title>
  <!-- EN: architect -->
  <Heyra_Story_Chiefarchitect.titleShort>建筑师</Heyra_Story_Chiefarchitect.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: {PAWN_nameDef} was not good at any work that requires hands-on. If it was in the sowing season, {PAWN_pronoun} might have more seedlings crushed than planted. If {PAWN_pronoun} was sent to do the cleaning, the room could end up messier than before. After being repeatedly criticized by {PAWN_possessive} fellows, {PAWN_nameDef} swore in anger to never touch several kinds of work ever again. -->
  <Heyra_Story_Clumsy.baseDesc>{PAWN_nameDef}不擅长需要亲自动手的工作。要是让{PAWN_pronoun}去田埂里帮忙，那{PAWN_pronoun}可能踩坏的幼苗比种下的还多。如果派{PAWN_pronoun}去打扫屋子，那房间可能会变得比之前更乱。在连续的恶评之下，{PAWN_pronoun}发誓以后再也不干某些活了。</Heyra_Story_Clumsy.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: clumsy child -->
  <Heyra_Story_Clumsy.title>笨拙稚童</Heyra_Story_Clumsy.title>
  <!-- EN: clumsy child -->
  <Heyra_Story_Clumsy.titleShort>笨拙稚童</Heyra_Story_Clumsy.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: {PAWN_nameDef} was not good at any work that requires hands-on. If it was in the sowing season, {PAWN_pronoun} might have more seedlings crushed than planted. If {PAWN_pronoun} was sent to do the cleaning, the room could end up messier than before. After being repeatedly criticized by {PAWN_possessive} fellows, {PAWN_nameDef} swore in anger to never touch several kinds of work ever again. -->
  <Heyra_Story_ClumsyD.baseDesc>{PAWN_nameDef}不擅长需要亲自动手的工作。要是让{PAWN_pronoun}去田埂里帮忙，那{PAWN_pronoun}可能踩坏的幼苗比种下的还多。如果派{PAWN_pronoun}去打扫屋子，那房间可能会变得比之前更乱。在连续的恶评之下，{PAWN_pronoun}发誓以后再也不干某些活了。</Heyra_Story_ClumsyD.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: clumsy child -->
  <Heyra_Story_ClumsyD.title>笨拙稚童</Heyra_Story_ClumsyD.title>
  <!-- EN: clumsy child -->
  <Heyra_Story_ClumsyD.titleShort>笨拙稚童</Heyra_Story_ClumsyD.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: {PAWN_nameDef} enjoyed outsmarting other people. {PAWN_pronoun} always wanted to beat other children in exams, competitions, or even games. Once, after losing five consecutive games in Go, {PAWN_pronoun} could not control {PAWN_possessive} emotion and started a fight with the opponent furiously. -->
  <Heyra_Story_Competitive.baseDesc>{PAWN_nameDef}享受智胜他人一筹的感觉。不管是考试、比赛还是游戏，{PAWN_pronoun}都力求打败对手。一次连输了五把围棋之后，{PAWN_nameDef}抑制不住自己的怒火，和对方打了起来。</Heyra_Story_Competitive.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: competitive child -->
  <Heyra_Story_Competitive.title>争胜骄子</Heyra_Story_Competitive.title>
  <!-- EN: competitive child -->
  <Heyra_Story_Competitive.titleShort>争胜骄子</Heyra_Story_Competitive.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: {PAWN_nameDef} enjoyed outsmarting other people. {PAWN_pronoun} always wanted to beat other children in exams, competitions, or even games. Once, after losing five consecutive games in Go, {PAWN_pronoun} could not control {PAWN_possessive} emotion and started a fight with the opponent furiously. -->
  <Heyra_Story_CompetitiveD.baseDesc>{PAWN_nameDef}享受智胜他人一筹的感觉。不管是考试、比赛还是游戏，{PAWN_pronoun}都力求打败对手。一次连输了五把围棋之后，{PAWN_nameDef}抑制不住自己的怒火，和对方打了起来。</Heyra_Story_CompetitiveD.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: competitive child -->
  <Heyra_Story_CompetitiveD.title>争胜骄子</Heyra_Story_CompetitiveD.title>
  <!-- EN: competitive child -->
  <Heyra_Story_CompetitiveD.titleShort>争胜骄子</Heyra_Story_CompetitiveD.titleShort>
  

  <!-- EN: Unlike normal Heyras whose horns channel the spiritual power of the land creatures, {PAWN_nameDef}'s horns have the affinity to the sea. This type of situation is very rare and considered a disease. In the other hand, there are also Heyras who thinks coral horns are cute due to their pink color and rounded shapes. -->
  <Heyra_Story_Coral.baseDesc>与一般聆族不同，{PAWN_nameDef}的角不与陆地生物共鸣，而和海洋生物有良好的相性。这类情况被认为是一种稀有的疾病。但也有部分聆族认为珊瑚角粉粉的很可爱。</Heyra_Story_Coral.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: coralize syndrome patient -->
  <Heyra_Story_Coral.title>珊瑚角</Heyra_Story_Coral.title>
  <!-- EN: coral kid -->
  <Heyra_Story_Coral.titleShort>珊瑚角</Heyra_Story_Coral.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: {PAWN_nameDef} ran a rice paddy. {PAWN_pronoun} always favored the high-yielding varieties than the high-quality ones as {PAWN_pronoun} wanted to save more people in starvation. -->
  <Heyra_Story_Farmer.baseDesc>{PAWN_nameDef}耕种着一片稻田。比起高级的品种，{PAWN_pronoun}更青睐高产的稻种。{PAWN_pronoun}觉得喂饱更多人才是最重要的。</Heyra_Story_Farmer.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: rice farmer -->
  <Heyra_Story_Farmer.title>稻农</Heyra_Story_Farmer.title>
  <!-- EN: farmer -->
  <Heyra_Story_Farmer.titleShort>农民</Heyra_Story_Farmer.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: {PAWN_nameDef} helped {PAWN_possessive} family from a very early age. {PAWN_pronoun} were assigned duties such as harvesting crops, collecting eggs and, occasionally, fighting the megascarabs that invaded the field. Unfortunately, the busy farm work took up the time {PAWN_pronoun} should have spent on study. -->
  <Heyra_Story_Farmerschild.baseDesc>{PAWN_nameDef}从小就帮家里人务农。{PAWN_pronoun}得负责收粮食，捡鸡蛋，偶尔还得驱逐闯进农田的巨型甲虫。繁忙的农活让{PAWN_pronoun}完全没有时间读书了。</Heyra_Story_Farmerschild.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: peasant child -->
  <Heyra_Story_Farmerschild.title>农家少年</Heyra_Story_Farmerschild.title>
  <!-- EN: peasant child -->
  <Heyra_Story_Farmerschild.titleShort>农家少年</Heyra_Story_Farmerschild.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: {PAWN_nameDef} inspected the vital energy that flows between heaven and earth. {PAWN_possessive} duties included locating mineral deposits, predicting the weather and giving instructions to the farmers. -->
  <Heyra_Story_Geomancer.baseDesc>{PAWN_nameDef}观察天地间气的流动。{PAWN_pronoun}能探测地下的矿物资源，预测天气，指引人们进行农事活动。</Heyra_Story_Geomancer.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: geomancer -->
  <Heyra_Story_Geomancer.title>钦天监监正</Heyra_Story_Geomancer.title>
  <!-- EN: geomancer -->
  <Heyra_Story_Geomancer.titleShort>监正</Heyra_Story_Geomancer.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: {PAWN_nameDef} worked in rich Heyran famlies. {PAWN_possessive} was responsible for supporting children's education along with wider mentoring. {PAWN_nameDef} also liked teaching children to bake cookies. -->
  <Heyra_Story_Governess.baseDesc>{PAWN_nameDef}为那些富裕的家庭工作。{PAWN_pronoun}负责教育这些家庭的孩子，提供人生的指导。除此之外，{PAWN_pronoun}还喜欢教孩子们烤小糖饼。</Heyra_Story_Governess.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: governess -->
  <Heyra_Story_Governess.title>家庭教师</Heyra_Story_Governess.title>
  <!-- EN: governess -->
  <Heyra_Story_Governess.titleShort>家教</Heyra_Story_Governess.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: {PAWN_nameDef} leads a hunt group of many less-experienced Heyra hunters. They challenge the most dangerous beasts, even the Insectoid.   -->
  <Heyra_Story_Huntmaster.baseDesc>{PAWN_nameDef}带领着一队猎人，挑战最危险的猎物。这之中甚至包括虫族。</Heyra_Story_Huntmaster.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: huntmaster -->
  <Heyra_Story_Huntmaster.title>猎师</Heyra_Story_Huntmaster.title>
  <!-- EN: huntmaster -->
  <Heyra_Story_Huntmaster.titleShort>猎师</Heyra_Story_Huntmaster.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: {PAWN_nameDef} was the purest kid among the peers. {PAWN_pronoun} had no bad thoughts and was willing to trust others, even if it caused {PAWN_objective} to be deceived many times. -->
  <Heyra_Story_Innocent.baseDesc>{PAWN_nameDef}简直是同龄人中最纯洁的，可谓是心无邪念。即便被骗了几次，{PAWN_pronoun}还是愿意相信他人</Heyra_Story_Innocent.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: innocent child -->
  <Heyra_Story_Innocent.title>纯真稚童</Heyra_Story_Innocent.title>
  <!-- EN: innocent -->
  <Heyra_Story_Innocent.titleShort>稚童</Heyra_Story_Innocent.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: {PAWN_nameDef} was the purest kid among the peers. {PAWN_pronoun} had no bad thoughts and was willing to trust others, even if it caused {PAWN_objective} to be deceived many times. -->
  <Heyra_Story_InnocentD.baseDesc>{PAWN_nameDef}简直是同龄人中最纯洁的，可谓是心无邪念。即便被骗了几次，{PAWN_pronoun}还是愿意相信他人</Heyra_Story_InnocentD.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: innocent child -->
  <Heyra_Story_InnocentD.title>纯真稚童</Heyra_Story_InnocentD.title>
  <!-- EN: innocent -->
  <Heyra_Story_InnocentD.titleShort>稚童</Heyra_Story_InnocentD.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: {PAWN_nameDef} has never forged a sword or a piece of armor. Instead, {PAWN_pronoun} made fine zithers using {PAWN_possessive} skill and craftmanship. -->
  <Heyra_Story_Luthier.baseDesc>{PAWN_nameDef}从未打造过任何兵刃，而是用超凡的手艺制作精致的筝琴。</Heyra_Story_Luthier.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: pacifist luthier -->
  <Heyra_Story_Luthier.title>制琴师</Heyra_Story_Luthier.title>
  <!-- EN: luthier -->
  <Heyra_Story_Luthier.titleShort>制琴师</Heyra_Story_Luthier.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: {PAWN_nameDef} practiced martial arts under a former Forbidden Army soldier. The trainning covered both armed and unarmed combat. As a result, {PAWN_pronoun} learned to perform deadly moves using a variety of weapons and developed a good physique. -->
  <Heyra_Story_Martialartist.baseDesc>{PAWN_nameDef}曾在一名退伍禁军手下学习武术。训练内容包括持械和空手战斗。经过多年的练习，{PAWN_pronoun}学会了多般兵器，身体也变得强壮了。</Heyra_Story_Martialartist.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: juvenile martial artist -->
  <Heyra_Story_Martialartist.title>习武少年</Heyra_Story_Martialartist.title>
  <!-- EN: martial artist -->
  <Heyra_Story_Martialartist.titleShort>习武少年</Heyra_Story_Martialartist.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: {PAWN_nameDef} practiced martial arts under a former Forbidden Army soldier. The trainning covered both armed and unarmed combat. As a result, {PAWN_pronoun} learned to perform deadly moves using a variety of weapons and developed a good physique. -->
  <Heyra_Story_MartialartistD.baseDesc>{PAWN_nameDef}曾在一名退伍禁军手下学习武术。训练内容包括持械和空手战斗。经过多年的练习，{PAWN_pronoun}学会了多般兵器，身体也变得强壮了。</Heyra_Story_MartialartistD.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: juvenile martial artist -->
  <Heyra_Story_MartialartistD.title>习武少年</Heyra_Story_MartialartistD.title>
  <!-- EN: martial artist -->
  <Heyra_Story_MartialartistD.titleShort>习武少年</Heyra_Story_MartialartistD.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: {PAWN_nameDef} periodically visited the nearby outlander settlements to import industrial products. These products were very profitable if sold to the Heyras. {PAWN_pronoun} has made a small fortune from the trade and was planning to expand {PAWN_possessive} business. -->
  <Heyra_Story_Merchant.baseDesc>{PAWN_nameDef}按期从外来者的定居地进口重要的工业品。这些产品非常好卖。{PAWN_nameDef}挣了不少钱，打算进一步拓展{PAWN_possessive}生意。</Heyra_Story_Merchant.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: merchant -->
  <Heyra_Story_Merchant.title>康食商贾</Heyra_Story_Merchant.title>
  <!-- EN: merchant -->
  <Heyra_Story_Merchant.titleShort>商贾</Heyra_Story_Merchant.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: {PAWN_nameDef} used to be the naughtiest of the kids around. {PAWN_possessive} pranks often went too far and caused a fight between {PAWN_objective} and the victim. -->
  <Heyra_Story_Naughtykid.baseDesc>{PAWN_nameDef}曾是最调皮的那一类孩子。{PAWN_possessive}恶作剧经常搞过头，使得愤怒的受害者对{PAWN_objective}拳脚相向。</Heyra_Story_Naughtykid.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: naughty kid -->
  <Heyra_Story_Naughtykid.title>调皮鬼</Heyra_Story_Naughtykid.title>
  <!-- EN: naughty kid -->
  <Heyra_Story_Naughtykid.titleShort>调皮鬼</Heyra_Story_Naughtykid.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: {PAWN_nameDef} used to be the naughtiest of the kids around. {PAWN_possessive} pranks often went too far and caused a fight between {PAWN_objective} and the victim. -->
  <Heyra_Story_NaughtykidD.baseDesc>{PAWN_nameDef}曾是最调皮的那一类孩子。{PAWN_possessive}恶作剧经常搞过头，使得愤怒的受害者对{PAWN_objective}拳脚相向。</Heyra_Story_NaughtykidD.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: naughty kid -->
  <Heyra_Story_NaughtykidD.title>调皮鬼</Heyra_Story_NaughtykidD.title>
  <!-- EN: naughty kid -->
  <Heyra_Story_NaughtykidD.titleShort>调皮鬼</Heyra_Story_NaughtykidD.titleShort>
  
