  <!-- EN: Although most Heyras deny the possibility to make a peace treaty with Rong, {PAWN_nameDef} thought differently. {PAWN_pronoun} spent years reading historical documents, and found that ancient Heyra and Rong share the same bloodline. {PAWN_nameDef} believed this is key to the peaceful coexistence of the two. -->
  <Heyra_Story_Peacecaller.baseDesc>多数聆族人都觉得与戎人之间没有和平的可能，可{PAWN_nameDef}不这么想。多年以来，{PAWN_pronoun}查阅了许多历史资料，发现聆族与戎人有共同的祖先。{PAWN_nameDef}相信这个发现是引导二者走向共存的关键。</Heyra_Story_Peacecaller.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: peace caller -->
  <Heyra_Story_Peacecaller.title>调停人</Heyra_Story_Peacecaller.title>
  <!-- EN: peace caller -->
  <Heyra_Story_Peacecaller.titleShort>调停人</Heyra_Story_Peacecaller.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: {PAWN_nameDef} has been hired to cultivate a strawberry field for many years. Box after box of nicely-grown strawberry has been shipped out of the farm, but {PAWN_nameDef} has never tasted a single one. -->
  <Heyra_Story_Peasant.baseDesc>许多年来，{PAWN_nameDef}都受雇于一个草莓园。一箱又一箱成熟的草莓被运出园子，{PAWN_pronoun}自己却一颗也没有尝过。</Heyra_Story_Peasant.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: peasant -->
