  <!-- EN: peasant -->
  <Heyra_Story_Peasant.titleShort>雇农</Heyra_Story_Peasant.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: {PAWN_nameDef} worked in the Imperial Pharmacy. {PAWN_pronoun} was knowledgeable in medicine and wrote several books using {PAWN_possessive} knowledge. -->
  <Heyra_Story_Pharmacist.baseDesc>{PAWN_nameDef}任职于御药房。{PAWN_pronoun}对药学的知识极为丰富，还将这些知识写成了许多册医书。</Heyra_Story_Pharmacist.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: imperial pharmacist -->
  <Heyra_Story_Pharmacist.title>御医</Heyra_Story_Pharmacist.title>
  <!-- EN: pharmacist -->
  <Heyra_Story_Pharmacist.titleShort>御医</Heyra_Story_Pharmacist.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: {PAWN_nameDef} has lived in an outlander settlement for several years and believed Realm of Heyra needed to be industrialized in all aspects. After going back to her hometown, {PAWN_pronoun} She persuaded the local official to let her lead a series of reforms. Sadly most of them were hasty and did not achieve satisfactory results. -->
  <Heyra_Story_Radicalreformer.baseDesc>{PAWN_nameDef}曾经在外来者的殖民地住过几年，觉得{PAWN_possessive}国家需要全面工业化。在回到故乡之后，{PAWN_nameDef}说服了一位官员，让{PAWN_pronoun}负责进行一系列的改革。可惜的是，这些改革大多过于仓促，难以令人满意。</Heyra_Story_Radicalreformer.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: radical reformer -->
  <Heyra_Story_Radicalreformer.title>激进改革家</Heyra_Story_Radicalreformer.title>
  <!-- EN: reformer -->
  <Heyra_Story_Radicalreformer.titleShort>改革家</Heyra_Story_Radicalreformer.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: {PAWN_nameDef} could not stand {PAWN_possessive} family being strict with {PAWN_objective}. After runing from home, the forest became {PAWN_possessive} hiding place. {PAWN_pronoun} managed to overcome the dangers in the forest and developed the ability to survive in the wild. -->
  <Heyra_Story_Rebellious.baseDesc>{PAWN_nameDef}觉得家庭管教过于严厉。{PAWN_pronoun}离家出走，藏匿进了一片森林。{PAWN_pronoun}在那里磨练出了在野外生存的技巧。</Heyra_Story_Rebellious.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: rebellious child -->
