  <!-- EN: One day, an Infestation scourged {PAWN_nameDef}'s village. {PAWN_pronoun} and {PAWN_possessive} family were scattered in the chaos as people were desperately trying to escape. After that, {PAWN_nameDef} had to survive alone. -->
  <Heyra_Story_Separatedchild.baseDesc>某日，一场突如其来的虫害袭击了{PAWN_nameDef}的村子。村人四散奔逃。在混乱中{PAWN_pronoun}和家人走散了。那之后，{PAWN_pronoun}只能独自流浪。</Heyra_Story_Separatedchild.baseDesc>
